85dc037797c7f230fc15c6a296d7b661459f34fb.query:
SELECT
                id,
                email,
                name,
                created_at,
                updated_at,
                github_id,
                google_id,
                photo_url,
                role
            FROM members
            WHERE
                name = COALESCE($1, name) OR
                email = COALESCE($2, email) OR
                role = COALESCE($3, role) OR
                github_id = COALESCE($4, github_id) OR
                google_id = COALESCE($5, google_id)
